		(property "Description" "The Espressif Systems ESP32-S2-DEVKITM-1U Evaluation Board is a  development platform for RF, RFID, and wireless applications. It features the ESP32-S2-MINI-1 transceiver with 802.11 b/g/n Wi-Fi operating at 2.4GHz, making it ideal for wireless communication projects. Powered by a 32-bit Xtensa single-core processor running at 240MHz, the board handles complex tasks with ease."
